1. AAP Survey Variablesc	
Create survey questions:

Question	Variable Name
To Intake	to_intake
Map ID	mapid
Transit	transit

Example input when launching the job:
to_intake: 1416
mapid: 4545
transit: 1313

These automatically become playbook variables.

2. Jinja2 Template (machineset.yaml.j2)

apiVersion: machine.openshift.io/v1beta1
kind: MachineSet
metadata:
  name: {{ cluster_id }}-worker-extra
  namespace: openshift-machine-api

spec:
  replicas: {{ replicas }}

  template:
    spec:
      providerSpec:
        value:
          apiVersion: azureproviderconfig.openshift.io/v1beta1
          kind: AzureMachineProviderSpec

          tags:
            to_intake: "{{ to_intake }}"
            mapid: "{{ mapid }}"
            transit: "{{ transit }}"
